    "description": "charting functional regulatory maps in plants.\n\nPlant Regulation Data and Analysis Platform.\n\nPlantRegMap, a portal for the regulation data and analsyis tools in plants.\n\nPlant Transcriptional Regulatory Map.\n\nTranscriptional regulations in PlantRegMap are identified from literature and ChIP-seq data, or inferred by combining TF binding motifs and regulatory elements data (see methods for more details). Users can select one of the three modes to retrieve regulations according to your requirement: 1) \u201cTF (retrieve targets)\u201d to retrieve the downstream targets of input TFs, 2) \u201cTarget (retrieve TFs)\u201d to retrieve the upstream regulators of input genes, and 3) \u201cGene (retrieve regulations among them)\u201d to retrieve the inside regulations among input genes",
